name: FIRST LOOK! Up Close with the WestJet 737 MAX 8 at Calgary Airport
description:
Huge thanks to a WestJet employee for allowing me to attend this event! Today, October 11th, WestJet held an event for employees and media with their Boeing 737 MAX 8. They currently have two 737 MAXes, C-FRAX (which I caught on its delivery flight) and C-FNAX which came in a few days after. FNAX was open to employees and media to look around it, while FRAX was being prepared for a special employee flight over the Rockies (which I also caught, video tomorrow). Enjoy this quick tour of WestJet's 737 MAX 8 (which still has that new airplane smell)!

Thanks for watching!
